article:
This is a growing 'list of territorial [[Catholic Church|Catholic]]
[[diocese]]s'. There are approximately 3,000 dioceses of the Church. Those
dioceses which are archdioceses are marked in 'bold type' and are also
separately listed at List of Roman Catholic archdioceses.
